title: Automotive Relay 150A SPDT
blurb:
When too much current isn't enough - 150A contacts for ultra high power applications such as multiple lights, high power audio etc, in a small package.
Specifications:
Contacts: SPDT
Contact resistance: 30m ohm max
Contact rating: 150A
Coil voltage: 12VDC
Coil resistance: 50 ohms
Rated coil current: 240mA
Operate time: 10ms
Release time: 5ms
Operational life: 100,000 cycles
